name: Logistical Delay (V)
Lore: 'The Empire''s tremendous military machine requires extensive coordination at every level. Slight errors in any step can quickly escalate supply delays.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. During the power segment of a battle, may use X Force to reduce a starship''s immunity to attrition by X for remainder of turn. Once per turn, may use 2 Force to cancel the game text of a [Maintenance] character or a senator for the remainder of turn.',
